12. S3 provider.

### 🔵 Sprint D — „pregătit pentru viitor"
13. DB: db.json → SQLite (repository pattern deja la punct).
14. Docker + docker-compose.
15. Logging structurat + teste.
16. Responsive mobil + onboarding.

